item.title: A little help with compile error
item.dc:creator: @majorclucker majorclucker
item.description:
@majorclucker wrote:

Hit New… > For Variable Name Type in “Classpath” without quotes, match the case.
For the value:

SET CLASSPATH=C:Program FilesJavajdk1.5.0_08in;%CLASSPATH%;.

Hit New… > For Variable Name Type in “Path” without quotes, match the case.
For the value:

C:Program FilesJavajdk1.5.0_08in;C:Program FilesJavajre1.5.0_08in

[br][size=1]Posted at: September 02, 2006, 02:23:01 AM[/size][hr]Did this work?
